========
barelibc
========

Mostly a stripped down version of musl libc 1.1.11 for x86-64 linux
only, will enter seccomp strict mode as soon as program started.

compile C program

  gcc -static -Bpath/to/barelibc/lib -o evil path/to/barelibc/lib/libc.a evil.c

compile C++ program

  gcc -static -fno-rtti -fno-exceptions -Bpath/to/barelibc/lib -include path/to/barelibc/prologue.hpp -o evil path/to/barelibc/lib/libc.a evil.cpp
